						<summary>

						<p>Hero-stone (No. V) set up in the Basavēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>Siṁgaṇa II A.D. 1210.</p>						

						<p>This badly damaged inscription is dated in the 1[1]th year Pramādi (Irregular). The month and the date are lost.</p>						

						<p>It records the death of a warrior in a fight; details are not clear; mentions Abbalūr.</p>						

						</summary>
